parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger occupancy sensor can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the deactivation of the passenger airbag, which can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag warning light comes on intermittently
the passenger airbag indicator light toggles on and off
the airbag system warning message appears on the dashboard
the passenger airbag sensor is faulty
the airbag system is malfunctioning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the propulsion system can cause the vehicle to lose power, making it difficult or impossible to accelerate, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power
the propulsion system warning indicator illuminates
the vehicle goes into backup mode
and the fuel generator is engaged.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the battery pack can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, making it difficult or impossible to operate, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The battery voltage suddenly fails
the vehicle stalls
and the propulsion system warning indicator illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle's systems to malfunction, making it difficult or impossible to operate, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The instrument panel becomes inoperable
the screen that displays speed
fuel remaining
etc. goes dark
and the vehicle's systems malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to malfunction, which can lead to injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The airbag sensor malfunctions
the service airbag light warning appears
and the airbag system disables.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the charging system can cause the vehicle to not charge, making it difficult or impossible to operate, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The charging system malfunctions
the vehicle is unable to charge
and the charging override/interruption message appears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to shut off while in motion, making it difficult or impossible to control, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The ignition switch shuts off the vehicle while in motion
and the vehicle is unable to restart.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Propulsion Power Reduction and Engine Unavailability
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden loss of propulsion power and engine unavailability can cause the vehicle to decelerate or stall, leading to a loss of control, accidents, or strandings, especially on highways or in heavy traffic.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly decelerates or loses power
the "Propulsion Power Reduced" and "Engine Not Available
Service Soon" messages appear on the dashboard
the vehicle stalls or cannot accelerate
the engine fails to switch from electric to gasoline power
the vehicle's speed is reduced to a crawl.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Faulty software and propulsion system issues can cause the vehicle to malfunction, leading to a loss of power, stalling, or deceleration, which can result in accidents or strandings.
symptoms: The vehicle's propulsion system malfunctions
the software update is required
the "Propulsion Power Reduced" message appears
the vehicle decelerates or loses power
the engine fails to switch from electric to gasoline power.
